{
  "id": "RAW_4efbda",
  "title": "ChatGPT 评估员工绩效，评得是真能力吗？",
  "url": "https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=Mzg4NDQwNTI0OQ==&mid=2247587038&idx=2&sn=f5606a87ee4affdcde5df10a818ccf25",
  "date": "2025-05-27 12:20:00",
  "author": "AI科技大本营",
  "siteName": "AI科技大本营",
  "content": "\n \n \n  <p data-mpa-powered-by=\"yiban.io\" style=\"max-width:100%;white-space:normal;letter-spacing:0.544px;font-family:-apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;margin-bottom:0em;box-sizing:border-box !important;text-align:center;overflow-wrap:break-word !important;\"><span leaf=\"\"><br></span></p>\n  <section data-mpa-template=\"t\" data-mpa-category=\"正文\" data-mpa-template-id=\"1440\" style=\"max-width:100%;white-space:normal;letter-spacing:0.544px;font-family:-apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;box-sizing:border-box !important;margin-bottom:0px;overflow-wrap:break-word !important;\">\n   <section label=\"powered by 135editor.com\" style=\"max-width: 100%;font-family: 微软雅黑;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">\n    <section style=\"max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">\n     <section style=\"padding:10px;max-width:100%;text-decoration:inherit;border-width:1px;border-color:rgb(240, 242, 246);font-family:inherit;border-style:solid;box-sizing:border-box !important;overflow-wrap:break-word !important;\">\n      <p style=\"margin:5px 16px;max-width:100%;line-height:25.6px;box-sizing:border-box !important;overflow-wrap:break-word !important;\"><span style=\"max-width: 100%;line-height: 26.25px;color: rgb(136, 136, 136);font-size: 14px;letter-spacing: 1px;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span leaf=\"\">【编者按】绩效考核季，越来越多管理者开始用大模型生成绩效评语，省时省力，甚至还觉得“说得比我好”。但你有没有想过，这种看似高效的操作，可能正在悄悄腐蚀你作为管理者最核心的能力？</span></span></p>\n      <p style=\"margin:5px 16px;max-width:100%;line-height:25.6px;box-sizing:border-box !important;overflow-wrap:break-word !important;\"><span style=\"max-width: 100%;line-height: 26.25px;color: rgb(136, 136, 136);font-size: 14px;letter-spacing: 1px;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"max-width: 100%;line-height: 26.25px;color: rgb(136, 136, 136);font-size: 14px;letter-spacing: 1px;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span leaf=\"\">本文来自科技博客 Stay SaaSy，以犀利的语言和第一手观察，提出一个令人警醒的观点：把关键管理工作交给 AI，不是进步，而是一种“职业肌肉”的萎缩。</span></span></span></p>\n      <p style=\"margin:5px 16px;max-width:100%;line-height:25.6px;box-sizing:border-box !important;overflow-wrap:break-word !important;text-align:left;\"><span style=\"max-width: 100%;line-height: 26.25px;color: rgb(136, 136, 136);font-size: 14px;letter-spacing: 1px;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"max-width: 100%;line-height: 26.25px;color: rgb(136, 136, 136);font-size: 14px;letter-spacing: 1px;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span leaf=\"\">原文链接：</span><span leaf=\"\">https://staysaasy.com/management/2025/05/26/AI-management.html</span></span></span></p>\n     </section>\n    </section>\n   </section><span leaf=\"\"><br></span>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"margin-left:8px;max-width:100%;white-space:normal;letter-spacing:1px;font-family:-apple-system-font, system-ui, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:normal;margin-bottom:15px;box-sizing:border-box !important;margin-right:8px;text-align:left;overflow-wrap:break-word !important;\">\n   <span style=\"max-width: 100%;font-size: 14px;color: rgb(136, 136, 136);box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span leaf=\"\">责编 |梦依丹</span></span>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"margin-left:8px;max-width:100%;white-space:normal;letter-spacing:1px;font-family:-apple-system-font, system-ui, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:normal;margin-bottom:15px;box-sizing:border-box !important;margin-right:8px;text-align:left;overflow-wrap:break-word !important;\">\n   <span style=\"max-width: 100%;font-size: 14px;color: rgb(136, 136, 136);box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span leaf=\"\">出品丨AI 科技大本营（ID：rgznai100）</span></span>\n  </section>\n  <p style=\"margin-left:8px;max-width:100%;white-space:normal;letter-spacing:1px;font-family:-apple-system-font, system-ui, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.75em;margin-bottom:15px;box-sizing:border-box !important;margin-right:8px;overflow-wrap:break-word !important;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"max-width: 100%;font-size: 15px;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">绩效考核季来了，我眼看着一些管理者亲手“砍掉”自己的职业上限。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left:8px;max-width:100%;white-space:normal;letter-spacing:1px;font-family:-apple-system-font, system-ui, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.75em;margin-bottom:15px;box-sizing:border-box !important;margin-right:8px;overflow-wrap:break-word !important;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"max-width: 100%;font-size: 15px;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">他们兴奋地分享：用 ChatGPT 起草绩效评语多高效！但这些捷径，正是他们永远学不会当好管理者的原因。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left:8px;max-width:100%;white-space:normal;letter-spacing:1px;font-family:-apple-system-font, system-ui, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.75em;margin-bottom:15px;box-sizing:border-box !important;margin-right:8px;overflow-wrap:break-word !important;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"max-width: 100%;font-size: 15px;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">接下来，我们来拆解为什么 AI 并不是管理的抽象层，而是一个“漏勺接口” ——你越依赖它，成长得就越慢。</span></p>\n  <section style=\"text-align: center;\" nodeleaf=\"\">\n   <img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-imgfileid=\"100055306\" data-ratio=\"0.10666666666666667\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/e57b4b49-7fa9-4db6-6176-aac6e4990800/public\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1125\" type=\"block\" src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/e57b4b49-7fa9-4db6-6176-aac6e4990800/public\">\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"margin-left:8px;max-width:100%;white-space:normal;letter-spacing:1px;font-family:-apple-system-font, system-ui, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.75em;margin-bottom:15px;box-sizing:border-box !important;margin-right:8px;overflow-wrap:break-word !important;text-align:center;\">\n   <span leaf=\"\" style=\"max-width: 100%;font-size: 15px;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 18px;font-weight: bold;\">绩效评语：不是作业，是修行</span></span>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"margin-left:8px;max-width:100%;white-space:normal;letter-spacing:1px;font-family:-apple-system-font, system-ui, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.75em;margin-bottom:15px;box-sizing:border-box !important;margin-right:8px;overflow-wrap:break-word !important;\">\n   <span leaf=\"\" style=\"max-width: 100%;font-size: 15px;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">绩效写作之所以让人头疼，并不是因为它难写，而是因为你还没成为一个真正的管理者。</span>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"margin-left:8px;max-width:100%;white-space:normal;letter-spacing:1px;font-family:-apple-system-font, system-ui, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.75em;margin-bottom:15px;box-sizing:border-box !important;margin-right:8px;overflow-wrap:break-word !important;\">\n   <span leaf=\"\" style=\"max-width: 100%;font-size: 15px;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">真正优秀的管理者，就像爵士乐手随兴而弹反馈旋律，张口即来，得体自然。那种“即兴的从容”，只能来自数千小时的“痛苦练习”：艰难对话、字斟句酌、面对人的不确定性还能稳准狠。</span>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"margin-left:8px;max-width:100%;white-space:normal;letter-spacing:1px;font-family:-apple-system-font, system-ui, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.75em;margin-bottom:15px;box-sizing:border-box !important;margin-right:8px;overflow-wrap:break-word !important;\">\n   <span leaf=\"\" style=\"max-width: 100%;font-size: 15px;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">绩效评语，是管理的浓缩精华：它要求精准的判断、体贴的同理心、和面向未来的战略感。</span>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"margin-left:8px;max-width:100%;white-space:normal;letter-spacing:1px;font-family:-apple-system-font, system-ui, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.75em;margin-bottom:15px;box-sizing:border-box !important;margin-right:8px;overflow-wrap:break-word !important;\">\n   <span leaf=\"\" style=\"max-width: 100%;font-size: 15px;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">一旦你把它交给 AI，你省下的不是时间，而是自己“练功”的机会。你的团队或许听到了“没问题”的内容，你却一点“教练值”都没加。</span>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"margin-left:8px;max-width:100%;white-space:normal;letter-spacing:1px;font-family:-apple-system-font, system-ui, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.75em;margin-bottom:15px;box-sizing:border-box !important;margin-right:8px;overflow-wrap:break-word !important;\">\n   <span leaf=\"\" style=\"max-width: 100%;font-size: 15px;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">老练的管理者知道：写绩效，不只是为了员工成长，更是为了让自己更像一个管理者。</span>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"text-align: center;\" nodeleaf=\"\">\n   <img data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/c97bff1b-06ca-46b1-9b8c-4c751e115400/public\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.10666666666666667\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1125\" type=\"block\" data-imgfileid=\"100055305\" src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/c97bff1b-06ca-46b1-9b8c-4c751e115400/public\">\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"margin-left:8px;max-width:100%;white-space:normal;letter-spacing:1px;font-family:-apple-system-font, system-ui, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.75em;margin-bottom:15px;box-sizing:border-box !important;margin-right:8px;overflow-wrap:break-word !important;text-align:center;\">\n   <span leaf=\"\" style=\"max-width: 100%;font-size: 15px;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 18px;font-weight: bold;\">AI 是助理，不是大脑的替身</span></span>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"margin-left:8px;max-width:100%;white-space:normal;letter-spacing:1px;font-family:-apple-system-font, system-ui, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.75em;margin-bottom:15px;box-sizing:border-box !important;margin-right:8px;overflow-wrap:break-word !important;\">\n   <span leaf=\"\" style=\"max-width: 100%;font-size: 15px;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">你可能会问：“工具不就是为了让我们变得更强吗？”</span>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"margin-left:8px;max-width:100%;white-space:normal;letter-spacing:1px;font-family:-apple-system-font, system-ui, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.75em;margin-bottom:15px;box-sizing:border-box !important;margin-right:8px;overflow-wrap:break-word !important;\">\n   <span leaf=\"\" style=\"max-width: 100%;font-size: 15px;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">没错，但区别在于“可依赖性”。</span>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"margin-left:8px;max-width:100%;white-space:normal;letter-spacing:1px;font-family:-apple-system-font, system-ui, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.75em;margin-bottom:15px;box-sizing:border-box !important;margin-right:8px;overflow-wrap:break-word !important;\">\n   <span leaf=\"\" style=\"max-width: 100%;font-size: 15px;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">真正的抽象层（比如内存安全语言、拼写检查、计算器）是稳定的，每次行为都一致，这样你才可以在它们之上建立技能。</span>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"margin-left:8px;max-width:100%;white-space:normal;letter-spacing:1px;font-family:-apple-system-font, system-ui, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.75em;margin-bottom:15px;box-sizing:border-box !important;margin-right:8px;overflow-wrap:break-word !important;\">\n   <span leaf=\"\" style=\"max-width: 100%;font-size: 15px;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">但管理型 AI 不是。</span>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"margin-left:8px;max-width:100%;white-space:normal;letter-spacing:1px;font-family:-apple-system-font, system-ui, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.75em;margin-bottom:15px;box-sizing:border-box !important;margin-right:8px;overflow-wrap:break-word !important;\">\n   <span leaf=\"\" style=\"max-width: 100%;font-size: 15px;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">如果每一个管理动作——一对一、述职汇报、晋升推荐——都通过 AI 来执行，那也许可以成为“真实抽象层”。但现实远未到那一步。</span>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"margin-left:8px;max-width:100%;white-space:normal;letter-spacing:1px;font-family:-apple-system-font, system-ui, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.75em;margin-bottom:15px;box-sizing:border-box !important;margin-right:8px;overflow-wrap:break-word !important;\">\n   <span leaf=\"\" style=\"max-width: 100%;font-size: 15px;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">当 AI 还无法稳定托底时，你一旦将关键事务交给它，学不会的永远是你自己。</span>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"margin-left:8px;max-width:100%;white-space:normal;letter-spacing:1px;font-family:-apple-system-font, system-ui, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.75em;margin-bottom:15px;box-sizing:border-box !important;margin-right:8px;overflow-wrap:break-word !important;\">\n   <span leaf=\"\" style=\"max-width: 100%;font-size: 15px;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">AI 用得对，是拐杖；用得错，是拌脚石</span>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"margin-left:8px;max-width:100%;white-space:normal;letter-spacing:1px;font-family:-apple-system-font, system-ui, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.75em;margin-bottom:15px;box-sizing:border-box !important;margin-right:8px;overflow-wrap:break-word !important;\">\n   <span leaf=\"\" style=\"max-width: 100%;font-size: 15px;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">有些事，本来就该痛。</span>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"margin-left:8px;max-width:100%;white-space:normal;letter-spacing:1px;font-family:-apple-system-font, system-ui, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.75em;margin-bottom:15px;box-sizing:border-box !important;margin-right:8px;overflow-wrap:break-word !important;\">\n   <span leaf=\"\" style=\"max-width: 100%;font-size: 15px;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">那种“费劲”的感觉，正是你大脑回路重构、能力升级的信号。</span>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"margin-left:8px;max-width:100%;white-space:normal;letter-spacing:1px;font-family:-apple-system-font, system-ui, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.75em;margin-bottom:15px;box-sizing:border-box !important;margin-right:8px;overflow-wrap:break-word !important;\">\n   <span leaf=\"\" style=\"max-width: 100%;font-size: 15px;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">让 AI 把锋利打磨成圆润，就像考试时偷看答案：今天轻松过关，明天寸步难行。</span>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"margin-left:8px;max-width:100%;white-space:normal;letter-spacing:1px;font-family:-apple-system-font, system-ui, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.75em;margin-bottom:15px;box-sizing:border-box !important;margin-right:8px;overflow-wrap:break-word !important;\">\n   <span leaf=\"\" style=\"max-width: 100%;font-size: 15px;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">管理场景下，AI 的使用清单</span>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"margin-left:8px;max-width:100%;white-space:normal;letter-spacing:1px;font-family:-apple-system-font, system-ui, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.75em;margin-bottom:15px;box-sizing:border-box !important;margin-right:8px;overflow-wrap:break-word !important;\">\n   <span leaf=\"\" style=\"max-width: 100%;font-size: 15px;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\">推荐使用的地方：</span></span>\n  </section>\n  <ul style=\"list-style-type: square;\" class=\"list-paddingleft-1\">\n   <li>\n    <section style=\"margin-left:8px;max-width:100%;white-space:normal;letter-spacing:1px;font-family:-apple-system-font, system-ui, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.75em;margin-bottom:15px;box-sizing:border-box !important;margin-right:8px;overflow-wrap:break-word !important;\">\n     <span leaf=\"\" style=\"max-width: 100%;font-size: 15px;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">筛简历：放心用，规则明确，AI 擅长大浪淘沙。</span>\n    </section></li>\n   <li>\n    <section style=\"margin-left:8px;max-width:100%;white-space:normal;letter-spacing:1px;font-family:-apple-system-font, system-ui, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.75em;margin-bottom:15px;box-sizing:border-box !important;margin-right:8px;overflow-wrap:break-word !important;\">\n     <span leaf=\"\" style=\"max-width: 100%;font-size: 15px;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">设计流程：大多数流程都有模板，AI 能起草骨架，你来添肉。</span>\n    </section></li>\n   <li>\n    <section style=\"margin-left:8px;max-width:100%;white-space:normal;letter-spacing:1px;font-family:-apple-system-font, system-ui, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.75em;margin-bottom:15px;box-sizing:border-box !important;margin-right:8px;overflow-wrap:break-word !important;\">\n     <span leaf=\"\" style=\"max-width: 100%;font-size: 15px;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">合规提醒：例行检查、自动提醒，让 AI 扫雷，你省心。</span>\n    </section></li>\n  </ul>\n  <section style=\"margin-left:8px;max-width:100%;white-space:normal;letter-spacing:1px;font-family:-apple-system-font, system-ui, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.75em;margin-bottom:15px;box-sizing:border-box !important;margin-right:8px;overflow-wrap:break-word !important;\">\n   <span leaf=\"\" style=\"max-width: 100%;font-size: 15px;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\">不推荐使用的地方：</span></span>\n  </section>\n  <ul style=\"list-style-type: square;\" class=\"list-paddingleft-1\">\n   <li>\n    <section style=\"margin-left:8px;max-width:100%;white-space:normal;letter-spacing:1px;font-family:-apple-system-font, system-ui, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.75em;margin-bottom:15px;box-sizing:border-box !important;margin-right:8px;overflow-wrap:break-word !important;\">\n     <span leaf=\"\" style=\"max-width: 100%;font-size: 15px;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">招人环节的“打动人”：招到人是管理者的核心战斗力，不能跳过练习。</span>\n    </section></li>\n   <li>\n    <section style=\"margin-left:8px;max-width:100%;white-space:normal;letter-spacing:1px;font-family:-apple-system-font, system-ui, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.75em;margin-bottom:15px;box-sizing:border-box !important;margin-right:8px;overflow-wrap:break-word !important;\">\n     <span leaf=\"\" style=\"max-width: 100%;font-size: 15px;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">团队会议：别把 stand-up、backlog grooming 交给 AI。你必须亲自参与，感受团队呼吸的节奏。</span>\n    </section></li>\n   <li>\n    <section style=\"margin-left:8px;max-width:100%;white-space:normal;letter-spacing:1px;font-family:-apple-system-font, system-ui, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.75em;margin-bottom:15px;box-sizing:border-box !important;margin-right:8px;overflow-wrap:break-word !important;\">\n     <span leaf=\"\" style=\"max-width: 100%;font-size: 15px;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">绩效评语：反馈是一门手艺，手艺不练，永远不会。</span>\n    </section></li>\n   <li>\n    <section style=\"margin-left:8px;max-width:100%;white-space:normal;letter-spacing:1px;font-family:-apple-system-font, system-ui, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.75em;margin-bottom:15px;box-sizing:border-box !important;margin-right:8px;overflow-wrap:break-word !important;\">\n     <span leaf=\"\" style=\"max-width: 100%;font-size: 15px;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">职业规划：可以让 AI 帮你发散思路，但方案一定得你自己打磨。</span>\n    </section></li>\n  </ul>\n  <section style=\"margin-left:8px;max-width:100%;white-space:normal;letter-spacing:1px;font-family:-apple-system-font, system-ui, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.75em;margin-bottom:15px;box-sizing:border-box !important;margin-right:8px;overflow-wrap:break-word !important;\">\n   <span leaf=\"\" style=\"max-width: 100%;font-size: 15px;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">一句话总结：AI 适合重复任务，或答案唯一的事务。</span>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"margin-left:8px;max-width:100%;white-space:normal;letter-spacing:1px;font-family:-apple-system-font, system-ui, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.75em;margin-bottom:15px;box-sizing:border-box !important;margin-right:8px;overflow-wrap:break-word !important;\">\n   <span leaf=\"\" style=\"max-width: 100%;font-size: 15px;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">但如果这件事需要你深入思考、权衡人性、判断模糊地带——那正是“管理者本体”的修炼场。别把它拱手让给机器。</span>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"text-align: center;\" nodeleaf=\"\">\n   <img data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/5babfca6-97d0-42f7-c02e-4377a7635e00/public\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.10666666666666667\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1125\" type=\"block\" data-imgfileid=\"100055307\" src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/5babfca6-97d0-42f7-c02e-4377a7635e00/public\">\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"margin-left:8px;max-width:100%;white-space:normal;letter-spacing:1px;font-family:-apple-system-font, system-ui, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.75em;margin-bottom:15px;box-sizing:border-box !important;margin-right:8px;overflow-wrap:break-word !important;text-align:center;\">\n   <span leaf=\"\" style=\"max-width: 100%;font-size: 15px;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 18px;font-weight: bold;\">网友热议：AI 评估员工，评的真是能力吗？</span></span>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"margin-left:8px;max-width:100%;white-space:normal;letter-spacing:1px;font-family:-apple-system-font, system-ui, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.75em;margin-bottom:15px;box-sizing:border-box !important;margin-right:8px;overflow-wrap:break-word !important;\">\n   <span leaf=\"\" style=\"max-width: 100%;font-size: 15px;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">这篇文章在 Hacker News 上引发了大量共鸣与争议，许多网友从亲身经历出发，对“ AI 辅助绩效评估”这一话题展开了激烈讨论。不少评论指出：比起担忧 AI 替代管理者，更令人担心的是 AI 让“坏管理”更高效。</span>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"margin-left:8px;max-width:100%;white-space:normal;letter-spacing:1px;font-family:-apple-system-font, system-ui, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.75em;margin-bottom:15px;box-sizing:border-box !important;margin-right:8px;overflow-wrap:break-word !important;\">\n   <span leaf=\"\" style=\"max-width: 100%;font-size: 15px;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\">观点一：绩效评估本身早已“坏掉”</span></span>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"margin-left:8px;max-width:100%;white-space:normal;letter-spacing:1px;font-family:-apple-system-font, system-ui, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.75em;margin-bottom:15px;box-sizing:border-box !important;margin-right:8px;overflow-wrap:break-word !important;\">\n   <span leaf=\"\" style=\"max-width: 100%;font-size: 15px;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">许多网友认为，绩效评估体系从根本上就是一种“政治化”“随意化”的产物，其设计目的并非提升员工表现，而是为了配合预算、升迁名额或法律合规需要：</span>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"margin-left:8px;max-width:100%;white-space:normal;letter-spacing:1px;font-family:-apple-system-font, system-ui, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.75em;margin-bottom:15px;box-sizing:border-box !important;margin-right:8px;overflow-wrap:break-word !important;\">\n   <span leaf=\"\" style=\"max-width: 100%;font-size: 15px;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">「绩效评估本来就很随意，结果反映的是当下公司需要什么。如果预算紧张，就没人值得升职；如果员工要加薪，就立刻变成‘明星员工’。」</span>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"margin-left:8px;max-width:100%;white-space:normal;letter-spacing:1px;font-family:-apple-system-font, system-ui, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.75em;margin-bottom:15px;box-sizing:border-box !important;margin-right:8px;overflow-wrap:break-word !important;\">\n   <span leaf=\"\" style=\"max-width: 100%;font-size: 15px;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">「我在管理岗时学到的一件事就是：你不能给太多人‘超预期’，否则他们会有晋升的要求。」</span>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"margin-left:8px;max-width:100%;white-space:normal;letter-spacing:1px;font-family:-apple-system-font, system-ui, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.75em;margin-bottom:15px;box-sizing:border-box !important;margin-right:8px;overflow-wrap:break-word !important;\">\n   <span leaf=\"\" style=\"max-width: 100%;font-size: 15px;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\">观点二：AI 不会让评估更好，只会让坏习惯更快</span></span>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"margin-left:8px;max-width:100%;white-space:normal;letter-spacing:1px;font-family:-apple-system-font, system-ui, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.75em;margin-bottom:15px;box-sizing:border-box !important;margin-right:8px;overflow-wrap:break-word !important;\">\n   <span leaf=\"\" style=\"max-width: 100%;font-size: 15px;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">不少网友担心，在管理者本身不重视“管理”的前提下，AI 只会成为写“模糊空洞评语”的高效工具：</span>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"margin-left:8px;max-width:100%;white-space:normal;letter-spacing:1px;font-family:-apple-system-font, system-ui, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.75em;margin-bottom:15px;box-sizing:border-box !important;margin-right:8px;overflow-wrap:break-word !important;\">\n   <span leaf=\"\" style=\"max-width: 100%;font-size: 15px;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">「真正有效的经理会自己花时间打磨评语，而不是说‘写一段中规中矩的内容’交给 AI 完事。」</span>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"margin-left:8px;max-width:100%;white-space:normal;letter-spacing:1px;font-family:-apple-system-font, system-ui, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.75em;margin-bottom:15px;box-sizing:border-box !important;margin-right:8px;overflow-wrap:break-word !important;\">\n   <span leaf=\"\" style=\"max-width: 100%;font-size: 15px;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">「AI 只会让糟糕的管理更高效，尤其是那些提供含混、相互矛盾反馈的管理者。」</span>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"margin-left:8px;max-width:100%;white-space:normal;letter-spacing:1px;font-family:-apple-system-font, system-ui, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.75em;margin-bottom:15px;box-sizing:border-box !important;margin-right:8px;overflow-wrap:break-word !important;\">\n   <span leaf=\"\" style=\"max-width: 100%;font-size: 15px;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\">观点三：AI 可以有用，但不该代劳“判断力”</span></span>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"margin-left:8px;max-width:100%;white-space:normal;letter-spacing:1px;font-family:-apple-system-font, system-ui, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.75em;margin-bottom:15px;box-sizing:border-box !important;margin-right:8px;overflow-wrap:break-word !important;\">\n   <span leaf=\"\" style=\"max-width: 100%;font-size: 15px;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">也有理性派观点认为，AI 在整理语言、结构化信息方面确实有帮助，但不能替代管理者对人的真实观察与判断：</span>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"margin-left:8px;max-width:100%;white-space:normal;letter-spacing:1px;font-family:-apple-system-font, system-ui, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.75em;margin-bottom:15px;box-sizing:border-box !important;margin-right:8px;overflow-wrap:break-word !important;\">\n   <span leaf=\"\" style=\"max-width: 100%;font-size: 15px;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">「AI 可以帮忙润色语言，但无法凭空写出有洞见的评语。」</span>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"margin-left:8px;max-width:100%;white-space:normal;letter-spacing:1px;font-family:-apple-system-font, system-ui, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.75em;margin-bottom:15px;box-sizing:border-box !important;margin-right:8px;overflow-wrap:break-word !important;\">\n   <span leaf=\"\" style=\"max-width: 100%;font-size: 15px;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">「让 LLM 提问并引导回答，最终整理成有用反馈，这种半自动化流程反而是个值得探索的方向。」</span></section><section nodeleaf=\"\" class=\"js_darkmode__172\" style=\"font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;font-size:17px;min-height:1em;box-sizing:border-box !important;text-decoration-thickness:initial;overflow-wrap:break-word !important;-webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent;outline:0px;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:-apple-system-font, system-ui, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;text-align:center;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;padding:0px;margin:0px 8px 15px;letter-spacing:1px;clear:both;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:1.75em;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;max-width:100%;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;\">\n  </section>\n  <p style=\"display: none;\"><mp-style-type data-value=\"3\"></mp-style-type></p>\n \n",
  "aiSummary": "文章探讨管理者过度依赖 AI 生成绩效评语的弊端，认为这会阻碍其关键管理能力的成长。",
  "oneSentenceSummary": "文章探讨管理者过度依赖 AI 生成绩效评语的弊端，认为这会阻碍其关键管理能力的成长。",
  "summary": "本文尖锐地指出，当前一些管理者使用 AI（如 ChatGPT）生成员工绩效评语，虽节省时间，却是在牺牲自身管理能力的提升。作者认为，撰写绩效评语的过程是管理者进行深度思考、同理心培养和战略判断的关键实践。将此任务交给 AI，相当于放弃了宝贵的“练功”机会，导致“职业肌肉”萎缩。文章区分了 AI 在管理中的合理用途（如筛选简历、设计流程）和不推荐用途（如招聘沟通、团队会议、绩效评语、职业规划），强调 AI 适合重复性任务，而非需要人性和判断的复杂场景。文末引用 Hacker News 网友讨论，表明关于 AI 评估员工的争议，并提出 AI 可能使“坏管理”更高效的担忧，同时也有声音认为 AI 可在辅助语言润色等方面发挥作用。",
  "mainPoints": [
    {
      "point": "将绩效评语交给 AI 会阻碍管理者核心能力成长",
      "explanation": "写绩效需要深度思考、同理心和判断力，是管理者修炼的关键环节；依赖 AI 会失去练习机会，导致管理能力停滞或退化。"
    },
    {
      "point": "AI 适用于重复性任务，不应替代复杂人性判断",
      "explanation": "AI 擅长规则明确、答案唯一的任务（如筛选简历），但不适合需要权衡人性、理解模糊地带的管理决策（如团队沟通、职业规划）。"
    },
    {
      "point": "过度依赖 AI 可能加剧管理问题而非解决",
      "explanation": "如果绩效评估体系本身存在问题，AI 只会让低质量、含糊不清的评语生成更高效，使得“坏管理”影响更大。"
    }
  ],
  "keyQuotes": [
    "把关键管理工作交给 AI，不是进步，而是一种'职业肌肉'的萎缩。",
    "你省下的不是时间，而是自己'练功'的机会。",
    "真正有效的经理会自己花时间打磨评语，而不是说'写一段中规中矩的内容'交给 AI 完事。",
    "如果这件事需要你深入思考、权衡人性、判断模糊地带------那正是'管理者本体'的修炼场。别把它拱手让给机器。",
    "比起担忧 AI 替代管理者，更令人担心的是 AI 让'坏管理'更高效。"
  ],
